MonitoringStation_Storage_Text_Agh::
	.string "AAGH!!$"

MonitoringStation_Storage_Text_Explain::
	.string "Huh, what?!\n"
	.string "Stop startling me!\p"
	.string "Wait, you're just a kid!\n"
	.string "You're not supposed to be here!\p"
	.string "You seem to have no idea about\n"
	.string "what's going either.\p"
	.string "Seconds ago, I was walking through\n"
	.string "the hallway on my way downstairs.\p"
	.string "Then all of a sudden, a ghostly\n"
	.string "figure floated past me.\p"
	.string "T-though I didn't get scared, I\n"
	.string "decided that it'd be safer to\p"
	.string "hide here for a while.\p"
	.string "Then I heard noises coming from the\n"
	.string "mechanical room, and everything\p"
	.string "turned dark.\p"
	.string "I can no longer reach my pals\n"
	.string "downstairs, because of the\p"
	.string "emergency doors that activated\n"
	.string "as a result.\p"
	.string "I guess the elevator malfunctioned\n"
	.string "and brought you here, am I right?$"
	
MonitoringStation_Storage_Text_RedKeyAdmin::
	.string "Look, I know we're bad guys, but\n"
	.string "maybe you can help us.\p"
	.string "The only way to get out of here is to\n"
	.string "use the staircase standing next to\p"
	.string "the elevator.\p"
	.string "However, to access the staircase,\n"
	.string "you will need a RED KEYCARD.\p"
	.string "Only two people in this base have\n"
	.string "been given such a key by our BOSS.\p"
	.string "One of them is the base's ADMIN, who\n"
	.string "oversees the monitoring office here.\p"
	.string "Then there is the EXECUTIVE, who\n"
	.string "has command over this entire base.\p"
	.string "Our EXECUTIVE, the coward, is likely\n"
	.string "hiding away inside his personal\p"
	.string "room downstairs.\p"
	.string "However, I saw the ADMIN at work at\n"
	.string "the monitoring office, which you\p"
	.string "came through to get here.\p"
	.string "It's likely that the emergency doors\n"
	.string "have him locked up inside his room.\p"
	.string "That means you will have to restore the\n"
	.string "power by reactivating the mechanical\n"
	.string "room.\p"
	.string "Honestly, you don't have much choice\n"
	.string "but to help us.\p"
	.string "After all, you're stuck here with us!\n"
	.string "Hehehehehehe!\p"
	.string "Now, get a move on!\p"
	.string "Restore the power and get that\n"
	.string "RED KEYCARD!\p"
	.string "Me? I'm just going to remain here\n"
	.string "while you do all the work.\p"
	.string "What else am I supposed to do!$"
	
MonitoringStation_Storage_Text_Done::
	.string "Huh, what?!\n"
	.string "Stop startling me!\p"
	.string "What are you waiting for?! Restore\n"
	.string "the power and get that RED KEYCARD!$"